:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af31fa93f94ec792fc01c8d7fc05cfcef5f3f7bf","tid":393594,"uid":24140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:21:00.000Z","msg":"終於有人講CSSA<br />\n<br />\n根本係共產黨海外分部 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb56f4de62d6d3032407228218fd9b7c4b540bff","tid":393594,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:22:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b590df939572f3b1f43817e41d3deb368f96bc6e","tid":393594,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:24:52.000Z","msg":"仲有各大學postgraduate association（神驅喺City搞退會嗰檔），全撚部都係支那人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cbaaec59f8e34560ab6e13c8d6d8305ccd022b0","tid":393594,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:29:51.000Z","msg":"香港中文大學內地學生學者聯誼會（CSSA @ CUHK）<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;成立於一九九七年，是由在香港中文大學學習的本科生，研究生以及訪問學者自發組成的<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>非政治性，非盈利性的民間組織</strong></span>，旨在為中大的內地學生，學者提供服務和幫助，解決實際困難，豐富業餘生活.CSSA是中大內地學人內部聯絡的紐帶，也是對外溝通的橋樑<span style=\"color: red;\">.CSSA目前與中央人民政府駐香港特別行政區聯絡辦公室（中聯辦），香港中文大學研究院，香港中國旅行社，中國（教育部）留學服務中心，京港學術交流中心，本港其他院校CSSA等機構，部門，團體都保持著密切的聯繫</span>，以保證及時轉達同內地學人在港學習工作和生活相關的重要消息，並提供信息指南。<br />\n<br />\n呢個<strong>非政治既民間組織</strong> 竟然把炮到有支聯辦同支旅社 BACKUP<br />\n咩關係大家心照啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6ac410644a8737c7475bb7f947a1256eb745cf","tid":393594,"uid":141804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:30:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"daeb9b7a644a256d5a8e005661ae5e17cc435aa3","tid":393594,"uid":40682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:31:41.000Z","msg":"其實跟返格式唔係應該係CUHK is not HK 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00694160561b028d1dee3e327ef7fac56da3354","tid":393594,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fsp.youthwant.com/images/580_937929436296087.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffsp.youthwant.com%2Fimages%2F580_937929436296087.jpg&h=7aeac4a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee6c704a346d241da5a5037d584766a714821906","tid":393594,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:44:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/228572/【民主牆之亂】內地生集會抗港獨收溫馨提示　內/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F228572%2F%E3%80%90%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E7%89%86%E4%B9%8B%E4%BA%82%E3%80%91%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%9F%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E6%8A%97%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E6%94%B6%E6%BA%AB%E9%A6%A8%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%E3%80%80%E5%85%A7%2F&d=s4u9Wt2qnufaM%2B%2B7vvEKeMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=d2f8c9ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/228572/【民主牆之亂】內地生集會抗港獨收溫馨提示　內/</a>"},{"pid":"a6d4d715a401aea6cf6d8ee24f99df3baaf0a5a0","tid":393594,"uid":58358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:44:47.000Z","msg":"點相起底，話唔定可以順便幫佢地個主席捉貪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3fb2fd1239447741b5940e28f169910af74a27","tid":393594,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b209527fc0e960541348c8c01b9248cea8d30eb","tid":393594,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1fc991b91934320509c6078924c457dc37422e","tid":393594,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T13:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae110bcf3f9682f71edb63b